hopobject.body: Can you put it on the scales, please? franceacheter.com McNish, Kristensen and Duval earned Audi its 12th Le Mans victory since its debut there in 1999, added a second consecutive hybrid-diesel powered victory to triumphs achieved with petrol and diesel power. The R18's 3.7-litre V6 TDI single-turbo diesel engine, further restricted to 483bhp this year, is backed up by two electric motors capable of transmitting the best part of 200bhp of additional power to the front wheels using energy generated under braking.
